            <p>My friends call me BMC, but my family calls me Brian.</p>
            <p>I am a 👧🏻 father, 👦🏻 father, 👩🏻 husband, 🗽 New Yorker, <a href="#designer">designer</a> 👨‍💻, ️<a href="#cycling">cyclist</a> 🚲, <a href="https://www.steelgills.com">PADI divemaster</a> 🤿, and <a href="#travel">world traveler</a> 🌎.</p>
